Over the past few years since launching the #BBG, my passion for helping women learn to live healthier lives through health and fitness has grown so much. My mission is to help as many women as possible achieve strength, confidence and happiness. The incredible BBG Community has had such a positive impact on my life and my journey and I am so grateful that the #BBG program has helped bring so many women together. I have been blessed with so many experiences to share my health and fitness training and advice with you all. I am SO excited because I have SO MANY new things coming your way that I have put together as a result of your feedback and requests. I truly believe that this community of amazing women is going to change the world for the better through health and fitness. I’m so excited to share this with you soon!! Let's do this! www.kaylaitsines.com/app #comingsoon follow @sweat 😉

Look, I've really nailed it down to the fact that I belong in a place that is summer all year round and its never cold or dark for too long hahahaha...seems fair!! www.kaylaitsines.com/app

Progress using my #BBG program! @bbg.evie She says "Today I got size 10 jeans and it's insane to think that two years ago I was in 18-20!! 🙈 my life has turned around since I started @kayla_itsines bikini body guides. I am such a happy and confident person now because of that. 🏃🏽‍♀️I have never felt better 69 weeks into her guides and 43 kilograms down!! 🏋🏽‍♀️ I recommend her guides to anyone and everyone because that girl on the left was drinking/smoking a lot, eating crap and did not exercise. I am the complete opposite now and after for the first time running 15 kilometres last weekend I know anything is possible! You can do it too!! If you're thinking of starting a life style change, do it please just don't give up, work through the sore muscles and push yourself outside of your comfort zone!! 😊💕" www.kaylaitsines.com/app #bbgprogress

Freshly squeezed orange juice....yes please!! Vitamin C ladies 😁 😁  To be honest, oranges remind me of netball games. As I'm writing this, I remember that some people don't know what netball is!! This absolutely cracked me up when I went to America. I'm going to pull up the Google definition....here we go - "a seven-a-side game in which goals are scored by throwing a ball so that it falls through a netted hoop. By contrast with basketball, a player receiving the ball must stand still until they have passed it to another player" .....hahahahaha. SO if you didn't know, now you do 😎  You learn something new everyday, ladies!! hahaha www.kaylaitsines.com/app

Take a second to breathe. A moment to yourself.  I was listening to a meditation app today and it really helped me. It said if you want to wind down, close your eyes, take a few deep breaths and play your entire day over in your head from when you woke up to this very moment. Once you get to the present moment, take 3 BIG deep breaths and open your eyes slowly. Try it and let me know if it worked for you !! www.kaylaitsines.com/app #bbg
